{"word":"συνεπανίστημι","slug":"συνεπανίστημι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συνεπανίστημι</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to make to rise up against together.</i><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with aor2 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>, <i>to join in a revolt</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>; <el>τινι</el> or <el>ἅμα τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}